title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – May 17 2022

description:
Clay and Buck break down Biden's divisive Buffalo speech. MSNBC falsely accuses Tucker Carlson of racism. Nevada Senate candidate Adam Laxalt updates us on his race. PA Primary Day with C&B: Dave McCormick joins C&B with his closing argument.
